@startuml Take-Quiz
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam padding 5

title Take Quiz – Sequence Diagram

actor "George\n(User)" as george
participant "Quizzes\nPage" as quizPage
participant "Quiz" as quiz
participant "Server\n(Express API)" as server
participant "MongoDB" as db

== View Available Quizzes ==

george -> quizPage : navigates to /quizzes
quizPage --> george : displays quiz cards with\ndifficulty (Easy/Medium/Hard) and XP rewards

== Start a Quiz ==

george -> quizPage : selects "Stock Basics Challenge" (Hard, 300 XP)

create quiz
quizPage -> quiz : <<create>> Quiz(id=1, title="Stock Basics Challenge",\ndifficulty="Hard", xpReward=300)
quiz --> quizPage : quiz with 5 questions loaded

quizPage --> george : shows Question 1 of 5\nwith multiple choice options

== Answer Questions (loop) ==

loop for each question [i = 1 to 5]

  george -> quizPage : selects an answer
  quizPage -> quiz : submitAnswer(questionIndex, answerIndex)
  quiz -> quiz : check if answerIndex == correctIndex

  alt answer is correct
    quiz --> quizPage : true (correct)
    quizPage -> quizPage : increment score
    quizPage --> george : highlight answer green,\nshow "Correct!"
  else answer is incorrect
    quiz --> quizPage : false (incorrect)
    quizPage --> george : highlight answer red,\nshow correct answer
  end

  george -> quizPage : clicks "Next Question"
  quizPage --> george : shows next question

end

== Submit and Grade ==

quizPage -> quiz : grade()
quiz --> quizPage : score = 4 out of 5 (80%)

quizPage -> quiz : isPassing(score)
quiz --> quizPage : true (score >= 80%)

quizPage -> quiz : getXPEarned(score)
quiz --> quizPage : xpEarned = 300

== Award XP ==

quizPage -> server : POST /api/update-xp\n{email: george@email.com, xpToAdd: 300}
server -> db : findOneAndUpdate({email},\n{$inc: {experiencePoints: 300}})
db --> server : updated user document
server --> quizPage : {experiencePoints: 1500}

quizPage --> george : "Quiz Complete! Score: 80%\n+300 XP earned!\nNew total: 1,500 XP"

== Retry Path (alt: failing score) ==

note over george, db
  If George scored below 80%, the system would
  instead display: "Score: 40%. Review the modules
  and try again." No XP is awarded.
end note

@enduml
